\f2\b\fs32 friction head
\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 <!$Scr_Cs::2>
\f1\fs32 , and the pressure required to impart velocity to the fluid, known as  
\f0\fs24 \cf2 <$Scr_Cs::2>
\f2\b\fs32 velocity head
